  "text": "Yohimbine is an indol alkaloid derived from the bark of Corynanthe johimbe, a tree indigenous to Central Africa that has long been used in the treatment of erectile problems [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . It has, at least in rodents, also been shown to be a powerful enhancer of copulatory behavior [CITATION_3] .",
